{"word":"G4041 - περιούσιος - perioúsios - per-ee-oo'-see-os - Peculiar","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">περιούσιος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">perioúsios</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">per-ee-oo'-see-os</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Peculiar</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"சொந்த - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"that which is one's own, belongs to one's possessions"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From the present participle feminine of a compound of <a href=\"#/G4012 - περί - perí - per-ee'/4012\">G4012</a> and <a href=\"#/G1510 - εἰμί - eimí - i-mee'/1510\">G1510</a>; <i>being beyond</i> usual, that is, <i>special</i> (one&rsquo;s <i>own</i>): - peculiar.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}